# Egress allowlist (POSIX extended regex, matched against the destination host,
# case-insensitive). FilterDefaultDeny Yes in tinyproxy.conf makes anything not
# matched here a refused connection. Keep this in sync with the feed hosts the
# MCP tools reach (mcp_server/tools/*, mcp_server/nvd_client.py) and the LLM
# provider (agent-api).
#
# NVD (cve_lookup, seed): services.nvd.nist.gov
^services\.nvd\.nist\.gov$
# FIRST EPSS (epss_score): api.first.org
^api\.first\.org$
# CISA KEV catalog (kev_check): www.cisa.gov
^(www\.)?cisa\.gov$
# Exploit-DB CSV (exploit_check), may redirect to a gitlab.com CDN subdomain
^([a-z0-9-]+\.)?gitlab\.com$
# GitHub code search (exploit_check public PoC lookup): api.github.com
^api\.github\.com$
# OSV.dev advisories (osv_lookup): api.osv.dev
^api\.osv\.dev$
# Anthropic LLM (agent-api): api.anthropic.com
^api\.anthropic\.com$
